{"tid":2294582,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"好香豔！泫雅秀更衣室「爆乳親密照」　裸足踩上男友帥臉","createTime":"2020-11-21T06:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T08:05:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af932ba2e4fda890e9b6fdfd3279fa767bc5e496","tid":2294582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"南韓「性感小野馬」泫雅去（2019）年初因跟小兩歲的男友E'Dawn認愛而遭前東家解約，之後小倆口雙雙簽約到「江南大叔」Psy開的經紀公司P Nation，終於可以毫無顧忌地大方放閃。近日，他們又在社群網站曬出多張親密照，其中一張，泫雅裸足直接踩男友臉上，引起話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/21/2784254-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F21%2F2784254-PH.jpg&h=25bb8da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼泫雅跟小兩歲的男友E'Dawn。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/21/2784251-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F21%2F2784251-PH.jpg&h=54ec21e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泫雅近日受邀擔任內衣品牌代言人，開心在社群網站曬出自己穿上內衣爆乳自拍的畫面，男友E'Dawn在背後緊緊摟住泫雅，在另一張照中，E'Dawn躺在地上，任憑泫雅赤腳踩在她臉上，還露出燦爛笑臉，似乎很享受跟女友的小情趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/21/2894078-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F21%2F2894078-PH.jpg&h=b6e744b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼泫雅跟E'Dawn一起在更衣室自拍。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/21/2894077-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F21%2F2894077-PH.jpg&h=251fb077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人大尺度放閃也引發網友熱議，有些網友就認為「她自己可以，她和男友不可」，覺得泫雅自信展現火辣身材相當養眼，但男友頻繁出現卻令人很掃興，也有網友指出：「我就是覺得她男朋友能不能不要再出現了！獨立行走啊！代言也非要綑綁真的很煩。」"},{"pid":"5a7424b0be34d6751669275bbc6f8356c548cd73","tid":2294582,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"好撚sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d124de08f4bf8287b9f49e248ddbc8448afc5c34","tid":2294582,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"老g"},{"pid":"4799d637709e2fcb4ae27e72c21b4ffbb185ef4e","tid":2294582,"uid":73972,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"隻腳幾靚"},{"pid":"7fc9829bb1f39313eae55e54b74b852872fcef1b","tid":2294582,"uid":36378,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"玩腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a001dd884e0f64d0d89e10fc8b83f7d24d3c3ae","tid":2294582,"uid":109,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"老坑"},{"pid":"56dea248881d9cc9307f06075392dd6f885ac017","tid":2294582,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"樣衰老雞"},{"pid":"aacd42d741b140049d29e38ac63ede8a091160a7","tid":2294582,"uid":138736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"爆乳？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f907abe25f5d165ea448d045459a3d0b906dc808","tid":2294582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56dea248881d9cc9307f06075392dd6f885ac017","tid":2294582,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"樣衰老雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"Yes <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351cbc89f9b09caf3111912f3424cd2b2e99bcc0","tid":2294582,"uid":136770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:10:49.000Z","msg":"收到風彩瑛都成日同紋身佬咁樣玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c94f5c04ee8ae722c35af92d0caf8bf979